TargetTime = {} TargetAzimuth = {} TargetElevation = {} counter = 0 Range = 2000 PingDelay = 0 TargetCount = 0 TargetRedundancy = {} function onTick() counter = counter+1
output.setBool(1, false) if(counter > PingDelay) then counter = 0 output.setNumber(32,TargetCount) TargetCount = 0 output.setBool(1, true) Range = input.getNumber(32) end
for i = 1,8,1 do if(input.getBool(i) == true and TargetRedundancy[i] == false) then TargetCount = TargetCount + 1 TargetRedundancy[i] = true TargetTime[TargetCount] = counter TargetAzimuth[TargetCount] = input.getNumber((i*2)-1) TargetElevation[TargetCount] = input.getNumber(i*2) output.setNumber(TargetCount, TargetAzimuth[TargetCount])
else TargetRedundancy[i] = false end
end
end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth()/2 h = screen.getHeight()/2 scale = (w-2)/Range PingDelay = Range*120/1480
screen.setColor(0, 100, 0) screen.drawCircle(w, h, 1480*counter*scale/120) if(TargetCount > 0) then for i = 1,TargetCount,1 do d = 1480*TargetTime[i]/120 hd = d*math.cos(6.28*TargetElevation[i]) pos = hd*scale if(TargetElevation[i]<0) then screen.setColor(255, 255, 255) else screen.setColor(50, 50, 50) end screen.drawRect(pos*math.cos(6.28*TargetAzimuth[i]-1.57)+w, pos*math.sin(6.28*TargetAzimuth[i]-1.57)+w, 1, 1) end end end

i = input o = output s = screen initialized = false zoomInButton = nil zoomOutButton = nil zoom = 5
function onTick() if (not initialized) then init() end readValues() handleValues() writeValues() end
function init() zoomInButton = createButton():onPressed(function () zoom = zoom - 0.1 if (zoom < 0.1) then zoom = 0.1 end end)
zoomOutButton = createButton():onPressed(function () zoom = zoom + 0.1 if (zoom > 50) then zoom = 50 end end)
initialized = true end
function readValues() sw = i.getNumber(1) sh = i.getNumber(2) touched = i.getBool(1) touchX = i.getNumber(3) touchY = i.getNumber(4) end
function handleValues() local zoomInPressed = false if (touched and ((touchX >= 0 and touchX <= 8) and (touchY >= sh/2-8 and touchY <= sh/2))) then zoomInPressed = true end zoomInButton:handleEvents(zoomInPressed)
local zoomOutPressed = false if (touched and ((touchX >= 0 and touchX <= 8) and (touchY >= sh/2 and touchY <= sh/2+8))) then zoomOutPressed = true end zoomOutButton:handleEvents(zoomOutPressed) end
function writeValues() o.setNumber(1, zoom) end
function onDraw() if (zoomInButton:isPressed()) then screen.setColor(0,0,0,170) else screen.setColor(0,0,0) end screen.drawRect(1, sh/2-8, 6, 6) screen.drawLine(4, sh/2-6, 4, sh/2-3) screen.drawLine(3, sh/2-5, 6, sh/2-5)
if (zoomOutButton:isPressed()) then screen.setColor(0,0,0,170) else screen.setColor(0,0,0) end screen.drawRect(1, sh/2+1, 6, 6) screen.drawLine(3, sh/2+4, 6, sh/2+4) end
function createButton() local _counter = -1 local _counterLast = _counter local _onDown = nil local _onPressed = nil local _onUp = nil
return { onDown = function (self, callback) _onDown = callback return self end,
onPressed = function (self, callback) _onPressed = callback return self end,
onUp = function (self, callback) _onUp = callback return self end,
isNotPressed = function () return _counter == -1 and _counterLast == -1 end,
isDown = function () return _counter == 0 end,
isPressed = function () return _counter > 0 end,
isUp = function () return _counter == -1 and _counterLast > -1 end,
handleEvents = function (self, isButtonPressed) if (isButtonPressed) then _counter = _counter + 1 else _counter = -1 end if (_counter > 100) then _counter = 1 end
if (self:isDown() and _onDown) then _onDown() end if (self:isPressed() and _onPressed) then _onPressed() end if (self:isUp() and _onUp) then _onUp() end _counterLast = _counter end } end

sw, sh = 0, 0;
transpTicks = 0 transpTicksLast1 = 0 transpTicksLast2 = 0 transpFreq = 0
radarTargetTTL = property.getNumber('Radar - Targets TTL'); radarTargetsTable = {}
function onTick() radarActive = input.getBool(29) transpActive = input.getBool(30) transpPulse = input.getBool(31)
gpsX = input.getNumber(25) gpsY = input.getNumber(26) compassAngle = input.getNumber(27) radarDirectionInDeg = rad2deg(input.getNumber(28)) mapZoom = input.getNumber(32)
myDirectionInDeg = (-compassAngle + 0.5) * 360 distanceOnScreen = mapZoom * 1000; --zoom 1 = 1000m on the largest side of the monitor
--| handle transponder if (transpActive) then transpTicks = transpTicks+1 if (transpPulse) then transpTicksLast2 = transpTicksLast1 transpTicksLast1 = transpTicks; transpFreq = transpTicksLast1-transpTicksLast2 end else transpTicks, transpTicksLast1, transpTicksLast2, transpFreq = 0,0,0,0 end
--| handle radar targets for i=1,6 do if (not input.getBool(i)) then break end
shift = i * 4 - 3 distance = input.getNumber(shift) azimut = rad2deg(input.getNumber(shift + 1) * (math.pi * 2)) tx, ty = getPointOnCircle(distance, myDirectionInDeg + azimut - 90) tx, ty = math.floor(gpsX+tx), math.floor(gpsY-ty) radarTargetsTable[tx..":"..ty] = {x=tx, y=ty, ttl=radarTargetTTL} end end
function onDraw() sw=screen.getWidth() sh=screen.getHeight() cx,cy=sw/2,sh/2
--| transponser area if (transpActive) then --| 20 ticks = 1000m. 40 ticks = 2000m --| 20 * 50 = 1000m 40 * 50 = 2000m transpRadius = ((transpFreq * 50 - 250) / distanceOnScreen) * math.max(sw,sh) screen.setColor(255, 170, 0, 30) screen.drawCircleF(cx, cy, transpRadius+1) screen.setColor(255, 170, 0) screen.drawCircle(cx, cy, transpRadius+1) end
--| radar direction if (radarActive) then actualRadarDirection = radarDirectionInDeg + myDirectionInDeg x1, y1 = getPointOnCircle(1000, actualRadarDirection-90); screen.setColor(0, 200, 0) screen.drawLine(cx, cy, cx+x1, cy+y1) end
--| ship direction screen.setColor(50,50,50) x1,y1 = getPointOnCircle(1000, myDirectionInDeg-90+180) screen.drawLine(cx, cy, cx+x1, cy+y1) screen.setColor(200,0,0) x1,y1 = getPointOnCircle(1000, myDirectionInDeg-90) screen.drawLine(cx, cy, cx+x1, cy+y1)
--| my marker screen.setColor(200, 0, 0) screen.drawCircle(cx, cy, 1)
--| radar targets if (radarActive) then for key, target in pairs(radarTargetsTable) do screen.setColor(0, 250, 0) tx, ty = map.mapToScreen(gpsX, gpsY, mapZoom, sw, sh, target.x, target.y) screen.drawCircleF(tx, ty, 1) target.ttl = target.ttl - 1 if (target.ttl <= 0) then radarTargetsTable[key] = nil end end end end
function getPointOnCircle(radius, angle) return radius * math.cos(deg2rad(angle)), -- x radius * math.sin(deg2rad(angle)) -- y end
function deg2rad(angleInDegrees) return angleInDegrees * math.pi / 180 end
function rad2deg(angleInDegrees) return (angleInDegrees * 180 / math.pi) % 360 end
